---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Collections — Axiom Atelier">
  <section class="collections-intro">
    <h1>Collections</h1>
    <p>
      Axiom Atelier's work is organized into three collections, each governed by the same
      principle of disciplined subtraction — applied differently depending on scale, material,
      and intent.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="collection">
    <h2>Foundations</h2>
    <p class="collection-tagline">Repeatable pieces for daily use.</p>
    <p>
      The Foundations collection includes furniture and object pieces designed to be lived
      with — quiet, functional forms built from quarter-sawn white oak and Peruvian walnut.
      Each piece is made to order, one at a time, by hand.
    </p>

    <div class="piece">
      <h3>5-Votive Tray</h3>
      <p class="price">$89.99</p>
      <p>
        A single tray in quarter-sawn white oak and Peruvian walnut, sized to hold five
        votives. Simple, precise, and built to outlast trend.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="piece">
      <h3>Still Horizon Side Table</h3>
      <p class="price">$1,150</p>
      <p>
        An oak side table built around a single horizontal plane — proportioned to feel
        weightless despite its solidity.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="collection">
    <h2>Witness</h2>
    <p class="collection-tagline">Earth pigment paintings.</p>
    <p>
      A parallel body of work exploring the same principle of subtraction through paint
      rather than wood — earth pigments applied and removed until what remains feels
      discovered rather than composed.
    </p>
    <p class="coming-soon">Coming soon.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="collection">
    <h2>Bespoke</h2>
    <p class="collection-tagline">Commissioned furniture, made to fit.</p>
    <p>
      For those who want a piece built specifically for their space, Axiom Atelier accepts a
      limited number of bespoke commissions each season. Commissions begin at $1,200 and are
      scoped individually based on material, scale, and complexity.
    </p>
    <a href="/contact" class="button primary">Inquire About a Commission</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .collections-intro {
    padding: 80px 0 40px 0;
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .collections-intro h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .collection {
    padding: 60px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .collection h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }

  .collection-tagline {
    font-style: italic;
    color: #7a7a7a;
    margin-bottom: 25px;
  }

  .collection p {
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #2a2a2a;
  }

  .piece {
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding-top: 30px;
    border-top: 1px dashed #ccc;
  }

  .piece h3 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }

  .price {
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .coming-soon {
    font-style: italic;
    color: #a0a0a0;
  }

  .button.primary {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    border: 1px solid #161616;
    background: #161616;
    color: #faf9f6;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
</style>